snippet.textDisplay:
For no reason I got tears. The way they recorded the acoustic instruments, those little elements, and suddenly the guy introduced the analogue. Even the people who have the cheapest headphones will also be happy with the sound quality, So wonderfully recorded ❤ 
And the most important, The Lyrics, so simply written yet so powerful. Whenever I think about Swanand sir, Bawrah Man comes into my mind. Whenever Shreya Di and he was sharing the screen, I thought I hoped one day they would make a female version of Bawrah Man with Shreya Di. 
She, her presence is like a home to me. Whenever she delivers such peaceful songs, I feel I'm sleeping on her lap in my peaceful home. And that thought gives me tears all the time. May God bless her and take good care of her. You're home to me Dibhayi. Mine Forever...
